截至当地时间24日零时，意大利累计确诊157例新冠病毒肺炎感染病例，2人治愈出院，新增1例死亡病例，累计3例死亡病例。
By 0000 hours local time, Italy had confirmed 157 cases of pneumonia, 2 cases were cured, 1 new case of death and 3 cases of death were diagnosed.
据欧联通讯社报道，死者是一位身患癌症的年长女性，确诊被感染新冠肺炎病毒后不治。
The victim, an elderly woman suffering from cancer, died after being diagnosed with New Crown Pneumonia, the EU news agency reported.
意大利紧急民防部部长安吉洛·博雷利(Angelo Borrelli)表示，到目前为止，卫生机构尚未找到引发病毒扩散的“零号”患者。
Angelo Borrelli, Italy's minister of emergency civil defence, said health authorities had so far found no "zero" cases causing the virus to spread.
而此前一些地方已经对中国侨民或有过中国旅游史的意大利公民进行过病毒筛除工作。
Earlier, some places have carried out virus screening of Chinese nationals or Italian citizens with a history of Chinese tourism.
按确诊人数计，意大利已成欧洲疫情最严重、亚洲以外全世界疫情最严重的国家。
In terms of the number of confirmed cases, Italy has become the most affected country in Europe and the worst in the world outside Asia.
政府宣布11个北部城镇“封城”为抑制疫情扩散，意大利总理孔特22晚日宣布一系列紧急措施，封锁伦巴第、威尼托等地的11个市镇。
Prime Minister Kent announced a series of emergency measures Sunday night to block 11 municipalities, including Lombardy and Veneto, in an effort to contain the spread of the epidemic.
约5万人被限制出入，警方将加强管控，必要时会出动军队。
About 50,000 people have been restricted, and police will tighten controls and call in troops if necessary.
意大利政府指出，违反疫区封锁管制的民众，将被视为犯罪，会受到刑事处罚，最高将被判处3个月的监禁。
The Government of Italy stated that the violation of the quarantine control of the affected areas would be considered a crime and would be subject to criminal penalties, up to a maximum of three months' imprisonment.
总理孔特表示，视疫情发展情况而定，这样的严格管控措施可被套用在其他地区。
Prime Minister Conte said such strict controls could be applied to other regions, depending on how the epidemic unfolds.
他暗示，并不排除“意大利暂停签发申根签证”的可能。
He hinted at the possibility of "Italy suspending the issuance of Schengen visas."
这两个大区是意大利的富裕地区与工业心脏，占据全国GDP的30%。
These two regions are Italy's rich regions and industrial heartland, accounting for 30% of the country's GDP.
而包括金融中心米兰在内，伦巴第大区要求关闭当地全部学校、博物馆与图书馆，取消文化、宗教、体育等公共活动。
The Lombardy region, including Milan, has called for the closure of schools, museums and libraries and the cancellation of public events such as cultural, religious and sporting events.
23日的3场意甲足球比赛也被取消。
Three Serie A football matches on the 23rd were also cancelled.
由于旅游胜地威尼斯也出现了确诊，威尼托大区行政长官卢卡·扎亚（Luca Zaia）已宣布叫停2月8日至25日的威尼斯狂欢节。
Luca Zaia, the governor of the region of Veneto, has announced the suspension of the Venice Carnival from February 8 to 25 because the resort city of Venice has also been diagnosed.
从3月1日起，该地区禁止一切公共与私营领域的集会，中小学校、大学与博物馆也将关闭。
From 1 March, all public and private gatherings in the area were banned, as were schools, universities and museums.
奥地利暂停与意大利之间客运列车北京时间24日消息，奥地利联邦铁路公司（OBB）当地时间周日表示，已暂停了与意大利之间经由布伦纳山口（Brenner Pass）的客运列车服务，以阻止新型冠状病毒进一步传播。
Austria suspends passenger train service with Italy The Austrian Federal Railways (OBB) said Sunday it had suspended a passenger train service with Italy via the Brenner Pass to stop the further spread of the coronavirus.
该公司一位发言人表示：“经布伦纳山口与意大利的客运列车已双向停运。
A spokesman for the company said: "Passenger trains between Brenner Pass and Italy have stopped running in both directions.
”这一跨越阿尔卑斯山的通道是意大利、奥地利和德国之间一条重要且经常拥堵的客运列车路线。
The route across the Alps is an important and often congested passenger train route between Italy, Austria and Germany.
在宣布暂停之前不久，奥地利政府表示，已拒绝一列从意大利威尼斯开往德国慕尼黑的火车进入，因为怀疑车上两名旅客可能感染了新型冠状病毒。
The suspension came shortly after the Austrian government said it had denied entry to a train bound for Munich from Venice, Italy, on suspicion that two passengers were infected with the new coronavirus.
奥地利内政部长卡尔·内哈默（Karl Nehammer）周日早些时候说，一个应对疫情的工作组将于周一举行会议，讨论是否实施与意大利的边境管制。
Earlier Sunday, Austrian Interior Minister Karl Nehammer said a working group dealing with the outbreak would meet Monday to discuss whether to enforce border controls with Italy.
这种边境管制可以在一小时内建立起来。
Such border controls can be established within an hour.
奥地利内政部长称，该国现在有181例疑似新型冠状病毒病例，但尚未有确诊病例。
Austria's interior minister said there are 181 suspected new cases of coronavirus, but no confirmed cases have been reported.
中国驻意大利大使馆发出提醒北京时间23日，中国驻意大利使馆发布针对意新冠肺炎疫情发展加强自我防护的温馨提醒称，近日，新冠肺炎疫情在意大利发生较大变化，2月21日意卫生部紧急颁布卫生条例，要求14日内去过中国相关地区的所有人员，必须到当地卫生局（ASL）进行备案，根据卫生局工作人员指导在住所进行隔离观察并接受监督。
The Chinese Embassy in Italy issued a warm reminder of the latest outbreak of pneumonia in Italy, February 21, the Ministry of Health issued emergency health regulations requiring all people who have been to China's relevant areas within 14 days to report to the local health bureau (ASL) for record, quarantined and supervised at the residence under the supervision of the Health Bureau.
伦巴第大区暂停除公共需要和企业内部生产之外的商业活动，鼓励远程办公，暂停娱乐活动和儿童教育活动。
The Lombardy region has suspended commercial activities other than public needs and intra-enterprise production, encouraged telecommuting and suspended recreational activities and children's education.
新冠疫情发生以来，广大侨胞已经自觉开展了较为严格的自愿隔离措施，在疫情防控方面取得了良好效果。
Since the outbreak of the new crown epidemic, the vast majority of overseas Chinese have voluntarily carried out more stringent voluntary isolation measures, in the prevention and control of the disease has achieved good results.
请广大侨胞进一步增强疫情防控和自我保护意识，在现有自发、自觉举措的基础上，遵守意卫生部和相关大区政府颁布的卫生条例，提醒和帮助14日内从国内返意人员及时到当地卫生局（ASL）备案，同时采取必要的防护措施。
On the basis of existing voluntary and conscious measures, we will abide by the health regulations issued by the Italian Ministry of Health and the relevant regional governments, remind and help those returning from China to report to the local health bureau (ASL) in time within 14 days, and take necessary protective measures.
侨胞如出现疑似症状，请及时拨打意卫生部1500热线，寻求指导和协助。
If the overseas Chinese people appear suspicious symptoms, please call the Italian Ministry of Health 1500 hotline in time for guidance and assistance.
外交部全球领事保护与服务应急呼叫中心电话（24小时）：86-10-12308中国驻意大利使馆领事保护与协助电话：+39 3939110852中国驻米兰总领馆领事保护与协助电话：+39 3272862927中国驻佛罗伦萨总领馆领事保护与协助电话：+39 3357748753综合人民日报、央视新闻、环球网、观察者网等推荐阅读点击大图|韩国疫情何以突然暴发？点击大图|销量增100%，日均交易增400%，在线理财产品现秒空，风口真到了？。
